  "title": "School Nurse Jobs ( 3 to 4 days Week, Staggered shifts  ) # $32 per hour #HVN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Main Responsibilities</strong></p><p>School shift Hour Applied</p><p>Start 7 am and staggered </p><p>•             To develop and maintain a high quality of nursing care in terms of wounds care and sports injuries in the Clinics </p><p>•             To participate in the development and implementation of policies and protocols which safeguard children, promote healthy outcomes </p><p>•             To collaborate and develop strong links with pastoral care colleagues such as counselors, house parents and teachers.</p><p>•             To take an active role in the education and promotion of health and medical issues to students and staff on an individual and group basis. </p><p>•             Liaise and follow up with the school medical provider. </p><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><p>•             Registered Nurse with the Singapore Nursing Board</p><p>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>EA Personnel: Valerie Yong Kian Fung</p><p>CEI No.: R1103704</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
